==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Motet
<hw>Mo*tet"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., a dim. of
<ets>mot</ets> word; cf. It. <ets>mottetto</ets>, dim. of
<ets>motto</ets> word, device. See <er>Mot</er>, <er>Motto</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>A composition adapted to sacred words in the
elaborate polyphonic church style; an anthem.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

